name: Jaime L. Garcia
text: :(  Ugh. I was linked, so I had to read.    I was almost like "GAH, I haven't seen it yet, it better not be a Doctor Who spoiler!" Buti na lang hindi. I read the thing and it did not exceed my spoilerometer.    Hello to you all!  Cecilia Tizon , do feel free to raise the intelligence level of the conversation by talking about something more than pretty girls.  :P
